m spending the next 10 years developing a skil, day in and day out, what skill would that be? What would I want? "), mdx("p", null, "Storytelling. I want to be a storyteller. I want to tell stories. I realize I\u2019m not great at it. I'm really good at thinking. I can talk alot. I'm really good at boring people as I talk. At least I recognize that. This isn\u2019t a story, I can see that. I can see the holes and the warts. It\u2019s a start. Gotta start somewhere."));
}
